{"tid":1470441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支 那 航 空 即 將 取 代 國 泰","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:32:32.000Z","uid":6630,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd5b4a7bcee8c6d1a607df90f92e670f0682e28","tid":1470441,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"唔好再嘈應唔應該阻人上機住喇<br />\n無論你係想和你飛定係你飛，我覺得都好應該睇幾張圖<br />\n呢個係香港人嘅國泰股價<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bQGo4HU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbQGo4HU.jpg&h=725253d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n以下係中國四大airline 嘅股價<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXvX89S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXvX89S.jpg&h=0fa978b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3QFtwoc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3QFtwoc.jpg&h=0e9b7fee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzzJ4Jc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzzJ4Jc.jpg&h=b1203942&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tq3CpJd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTq3CpJd.jpg&h=c9326c05&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你冇睇錯呀，國泰跌到仆街喇，但係支那嗰四間升到火箭咁呀<br />\n就算從攬炒角度嚟講，而家繼續落去只會炒爆國泰，之後俾Air China進駐香港<br />\n成日話賽後檢討，希望我哋真係做到檢討，諗吓而家行動上有冇改善改進嘅空間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割席係必要，但係同時不斷反省不斷思考，先可以繼續進步</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辛苦晒各位機場手足，一齊諗計再努力啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec885c6a06a7f8d07c6cb3208a474fff9bda1ee","tid":1470441,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"【重要通知】抗爭不割蓆手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請參閱"},{"pid":"b80